"upasaṅkamitabbā pātimokkhuddesāyā”’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.25"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.48"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc171"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.25.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, aññataro mahābrahmā mama cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya "
"seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā "
"bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—brahmaloke antarahito mama purato pāturahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so, bhikkhave, mahābrahmā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yenāhaṃ "
"tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.3"
msgid "‘evametaṃ, bhagavā, evametaṃ, sugata."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.4"
msgid ""
"Mahā kho, bhante, etarahi bhikkhusaṅgho bandhumatiyā rājadhāniyā paṭivasati "
"aṭṭhasaṭṭhibhikkhusatasahassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.5"
msgid "Anujānātu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhū—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.6"
msgid ""
"caratha, bhikkhave, cārikaṃ bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya "
"atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.7"
msgid "mā ekena dve agamittha;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.8"
msgid "desetha, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.9"
msgid ""
"santi sattā apparajakkhajātikā, assavanatā dhammassa parihāyanti, "
"bhavissanti dhammassa aññātāroti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.10"
msgid ""
"Api ca, bhante, mayaṃ tathā karissāma, yathā bhikkhū channaṃ channaṃ "
"vassānaṃ accayena bandhumatiṃ rājadhāniṃ upasaṅkamissanti "
"pātimokkhuddesāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.11"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, so mahābrahmā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.25.12"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tattheva antaradhāyi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc172"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.26.1"
msgid ""
"‘Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, caratha cārikaṃ bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya "
"lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.2"
msgid "mā ekena dve agamittha;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.3"
msgid ""
"desetha, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ "
"sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāsetha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.4"
msgid "Santi sattā apparajakkhajātikā, assavanatā dhammassa parihāyanti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.5"
msgid "bhavissanti dhammassa aññātāro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.6"
msgid ""
"Api ca, bhikkhave, channaṃ channaṃ vassānaṃ accayena bandhumatī rājadhānī "
"upasaṅkamitabbā pātimokkhuddesāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.26.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhū yebhuyyena ekāheneva janapadacārikaṃ pakkamiṃsu."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.27"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.49"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc173"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.27.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena jambudīpe caturāsīti āvāsasahassāni honti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.2"
msgid "Ekamhi hi vasse nikkhante devatā saddamanussāvesuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.3"
msgid "‘nikkhantaṃ kho, mārisā, ekaṃ vassaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.4"
msgid "pañca dāni vassāni sesāni;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.5"
msgid ""
"pañcannaṃ vassānaṃ accayena bandhumatī rājadhānī upasaṅkamitabbā "
"pātimokkhuddesāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.6"
msgid "Dvīsu vassesu nikkhantesu …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.7"
msgid "tīsu vassesu nikkhantesu …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.8"
msgid "catūsu vassesu nikkhantesu …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.9"
msgid "pañcasu vassesu nikkhantesu devatā saddamanussāvesuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.10"
msgid "‘nikkhantāni kho, mārisā, pañcavassāni;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.11"
msgid "ekaṃ dāni vassaṃ sesaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.12"
msgid ""
"ekassa vassassa accayena bandhumatī rājadhānī upasaṅkamitabbā "
"pātimokkhuddesāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.13"
msgid "Chasu vassesu nikkhantesu devatā saddamanussāvesuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.14"
msgid "‘nikkhantāni kho, mārisā, chabbassāni, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.15"
msgid "samayo dāni bandhumatiṃ rājadhāniṃ upasaṅkamituṃ pātimokkhuddesāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.27.16"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū appekacce sakena iddhānubhāvena appekacce "
"devatānaṃ iddhānubhāvena ekāheneva bandhumatiṃ rājadhāniṃ upasaṅkamiṃsu "
"pātimokkhuddesāyāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc174"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.1"
msgid ""
"Tatra sudaṃ, bhikkhave, vipassī bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho bhikkhusaṅghe "
"evaṃ pātimokkhaṃ uddisati:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc175"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.2"
msgid "‘Khantī paramaṃ tapo titikkhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.3"
msgid "Nibbānaṃ paramaṃ vadanti buddhā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.4"
msgid "Na hi pabbajito parūpaghātī,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.5"
msgid "Na samaṇo hoti paraṃ viheṭhayanto."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc176"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.6"
msgid "Sabbapāpassa akaraṇaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.7"
msgid "kusalassa upasampadā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.8"
msgid "Sacittapariyodapanaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.9"
msgid "etaṃ buddhānasāsanaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.50"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc177"></a>
#. VAR: Anūpavādo anūpaghāto → anupavādo anupaghāto (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.10"
msgid "Anūpavādo anūpaghāto,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.11"
msgid "Pātimokkhe ca saṃvaro;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.12"
msgid "Mattaññutā ca bhattasmiṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.13"
msgid "Pantañca sayanāsanaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.14"
msgid "Adhicitte ca āyogo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.15"
msgid "Etaṃ buddhānasāsanan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><h2>
msgctxt "dn14:3.28.16"
msgid "17. Devatārocana"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.29"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.51"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc178"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.29.1"
msgid ""
"Ekamidāhaṃ, bhikkhave, samayaṃ ukkaṭṭhāyaṃ viharāmi subhagavane sālarājamūle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko "
"udapādi:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: anāvutthapubbo → anaj­jhā­vuttha­pubbo (bj) | anaj­jhā­vuṭṭha­pubbo (mr)
msgctxt "dn14:3.29.3"
msgid ""
"‘na kho so sattāvāso sulabharūpo, yo mayā anāvutthapubbo iminā dīghena "
"addhunā aññatra suddhāvāsehi devehi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.4"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena suddhāvāsā devā tenupasaṅkameyyan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.5"
msgid ""
"Atha khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ "
"pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—ukkaṭṭhāyaṃ subhagavane "
"sālarājamūle antarahito avihesu devesu pāturahosiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.6"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃ, bhikkhave, devanikāye anekāni devatāsahassāni anekāni "
"devatāsatasahassāni yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, tā devatā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.7"
msgid ""
"‘ito so, mārisā, ekanavutikappe yaṃ vipassī bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"loke udapādi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.8"
msgid ""
"Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho khattiyo jātiyā ahosi, "
"khattiyakule udapādi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.9"
msgid "Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho koṇḍañño gottena ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.10"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa asītivassasahassāni "
"āyuppamāṇaṃ ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.11"
msgid ""
"Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho pāṭaliyā mūle abhisambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.12"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa khaṇḍatissaṃ nāma "
"sāvakayugaṃ ahosi aggaṃ bhaddayugaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.13"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa tayo sāvakānaṃ "
"sannipātā ahesuṃ. Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi "
"aṭṭhasaṭṭhibhikkhusatasahassaṃ. Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi "
"bhikkhusatasahassaṃ. Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi asītibhikkhusahassāni. "
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa ime tayo sāvakānaṃ "
"sannipātā ahesuṃ sabbesaṃyeva khīṇāsavānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.14"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa asoko nāma bhikkhu "
"upaṭṭhāko ahosi aggupaṭṭhāko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.15"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa bandhumā nāma rājā "
"pitā ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.16"
msgid "Bandhumatī nāma devī mātā ahosi janetti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.17"
msgid "Bandhumassa rañño bandhumatī nāma nagaraṃ rājadhānī ahosi."
msgstr ""

# This is basically a table of contents for any Buddha biography.
msgctxt "dn14:3.29.18"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa evaṃ abhinikkhamanaṃ "
"ahosi evaṃ pabbajjā evaṃ padhānaṃ evaṃ abhisambodhi evaṃ "
"dhammacakkappavattanaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.29.19"
msgid ""
"Te mayaṃ, mārisā, vipassimhi bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ caritvā kāmesu "
"kāmacchandaṃ virājetvā idhūpapannā’ti …"
msgstr ""

# While this is absent here, they are all mentioned below, and comm says they should be included here. This must be just a clumsy abbreviation.
msgctxt "dn14:3.29.20"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

# In PTS, unlike MS, the deities who came to see the Buddha are numbered as “hundreds”, which seems more reasonable. RD has this, while MW does not.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.30"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.52"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc179"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.30.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃyeva kho, bhikkhave, devanikāye anekāni devatāsahassāni anekāni "
"devatāsatasahassāni yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, tā devatā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.2"
msgid ""
"‘imasmiṃyeva kho, mārisā, bhaddakappe bhagavā etarahi arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"loke uppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.3"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, khattiyo jātiyā khattiyakule uppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.4"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, gotamo gottena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.5"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, appakaṃ āyuppamāṇaṃ parittaṃ lahukaṃ yo ciraṃ jīvati, so "
"vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.6"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, assatthassa mūle abhisambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.7"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, sāriputtamoggallānaṃ nāma sāvakayugaṃ ahosi aggaṃ "
"bhaddayugaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.8"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi aḍḍhateḷasāni "
"bhikkhusatāni. Bhagavato, mārisā, ayaṃ eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi "
"sabbesaṃyeva khīṇāsavānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.9"
msgid "Bhagavato, mārisā, ānando nāma bhikkhu upaṭṭhāko ahosi aggupaṭṭhāko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.10"
msgid "Bhagavato, mārisā, suddhodano nāma rājā pitā ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.11"
msgid "Māyā nāma devī mātā ahosi janetti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.12"
msgid "Kapilavatthu nāma nagaraṃ rājadhānī ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.13"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, evaṃ abhinikkhamanaṃ ahosi evaṃ pabbajjā evaṃ padhānaṃ "
"evaṃ abhisambodhi evaṃ dhammacakkappavattanaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.30.14"
msgid ""
"Te mayaṃ, mārisā, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ caritvā kāmesu kāmacchandaṃ "
"virājetvā idhūpapannā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.31"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc180"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.31.1"
msgid ""
"Atha khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, avihehi devehi saddhiṃ yena atappā devā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.2"
msgid ""
"atha khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, avihehi ca devehi atappehi ca devehi saddhiṃ yena "
"sudassā devā tenupasaṅkamiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.53"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc181"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.31.3"
msgid ""
"Atha khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, avihehi ca devehi atappehi ca devehi sudassehi ca "
"devehi saddhiṃ yena sudassī devā tenupasaṅkamiṃ. Atha khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, "
"avihehi ca devehi atappehi ca devehi sudassehi ca devehi sudassīhi ca devehi "
"saddhiṃ yena akaniṭṭhā devā tenupasaṅkamiṃ. Tasmiṃ, bhikkhave, devanikāye "
"anekāni devatāsahassāni anekāni devatāsatasahassāni yenāhaṃ "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu, upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. "
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, tā devatā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "dn14:3.31.4"
msgid ""
"‘ito so, mārisā, ekanavutikappe yaṃ vipassī bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"loke udapādi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.5"
msgid "Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho khattiyo jātiyā ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.6"
msgid "Khattiyakule udapādi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.7"
msgid "Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho koṇḍañño gottena ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.8"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa asītivassasahassāni "
"āyuppamāṇaṃ ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.9"
msgid ""
"Vipassī, mārisā, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho pāṭaliyā mūle abhisambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.10"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa khaṇḍatissaṃ nāma "
"sāvakayugaṃ ahosi aggaṃ bhaddayugaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.11"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa tayo sāvakānaṃ "
"sannipātā ahesuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.12"
msgid "Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi aṭṭhasaṭṭhibhikkhusatasahassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.13"
msgid "Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi bhikkhusatasahassaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.14"
msgid "Eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi asītibhikkhusahassāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.15"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa ime tayo sāvakānaṃ "
"sannipātā ahesuṃ sabbesaṃyeva khīṇāsavānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.16"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa asoko nāma bhikkhu "
"upaṭṭhāko ahosi aggupaṭṭhāko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.17"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa bandhumā nāma rājā "
"pitā ahosi bandhumatī nāma devī mātā ahosi janetti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.18"
msgid "Bandhumassa rañño bandhumatī nāma nagaraṃ rājadhānī ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.19"
msgid ""
"Vipassissa, mārisā, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa evaṃ abhinikkhamanaṃ "
"ahosi evaṃ pabbajjā evaṃ padhānaṃ evaṃ abhisambodhi, evaṃ "
"dhammacakkappavattanaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.20"
msgid ""
"Te mayaṃ, mārisā, vipassimhi bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ caritvā kāmesu "
"kāmacchandaṃ virājetvā idhūpapannā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.21"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃyeva kho, bhikkhave, devanikāye anekāni devatāsahassāni anekāni "
"devatāsatasahassāni yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, tā devatā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.22"
msgid "‘ito so, mārisā, ekatiṃse kappe yaṃ sikhī bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.23"
msgid ""
"te mayaṃ, mārisā, sikhimhi bhagavati tasmiññeva kho, mārisā, ekatiṃse kappe "
"yaṃ vessabhū bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.24"
msgid "te mayaṃ, mārisā, vessabhumhi bhagavati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.25"
msgid ""
"imasmiṃyeva kho, mārisā, bhaddakappe kakusandho koṇāgamano kassapo bhagavā … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.31.26"
msgid ""
"te mayaṃ, mārisā, kakusandhamhi koṇāgamanamhi kassapamhi bhagavati "
"brahmacariyaṃ caritvā kāmesu kāmacchandaṃ virājetvā idhūpapannā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.32"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc182"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.32.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmiṃyeva kho, bhikkhave, devanikāye anekāni devatāsahassāni anekāni "
"devatāsatasahassāni yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, tā devatā maṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.2"
msgid ""
"‘imasmiṃyeva kho, mārisā, bhaddakappe bhagavā etarahi arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"loke uppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.3"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, khattiyo jātiyā, khattiyakule uppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.4"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, gotamo gottena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.5"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, appakaṃ āyuppamāṇaṃ parittaṃ lahukaṃ yo ciraṃ jīvati, so "
"vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.6"
msgid "Bhagavā, mārisā, assatthassa mūle abhisambuddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.7"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, sāriputtamoggallānaṃ nāma sāvakayugaṃ ahosi aggaṃ "
"bhaddayugaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.8"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi aḍḍhateḷasāni bhikkhusatāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.9"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, ayaṃ eko sāvakānaṃ sannipāto ahosi sabbesaṃyeva "
"khīṇāsavānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.10"
msgid "Bhagavato, mārisā, ānando nāma bhikkhu upaṭṭhāko aggupaṭṭhāko ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.11"
msgid "Bhagavato, mārisā, suddhodano nāma rājā pitā ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.12"
msgid "Māyā nāma devī mātā ahosi janetti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.13"
msgid "Kapilavatthu nāma nagaraṃ rājadhānī ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.14"
msgid ""
"Bhagavato, mārisā, evaṃ abhinikkhamanaṃ ahosi, evaṃ pabbajjā, evaṃ padhānaṃ, "
"evaṃ abhisambodhi, evaṃ dhammacakkappavattanaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.32.15"
msgid ""
"Te mayaṃ, mārisā, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ caritvā kāmesu kāmacchandaṃ "
"virājetvā idhūpapannā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3.33"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.54"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc183"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.33.1"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, bhikkhave, tathāgatassevesā dhammadhātu suppaṭividdhā, yassā "
"dhammadhātuyā suppaṭividdhattā tathāgato atīte buddhe parinibbute "
"chinnapapañce chinnavaṭume pariyādinnavaṭṭe sabbadukkhavītivatte jātitopi "
"anussarati, nāmatopi anussarati, gottatopi anussarati, āyuppamāṇatopi "
"anussarati, sāvakayugatopi anussarati, sāvakasannipātatopi anussarati ‘"
"evaṃjaccā te bhagavanto ahesuṃ’ itipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.33.2"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃnāmā evaṅgottā evaṃsīlā evaṃdhammā evaṃpaññā evaṃvihārī evaṃvimuttā te "
"bhagavanto ahesuṃ’ itipīti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc184"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.33.3"
msgid ""
"Devatāpi tathāgatassa etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ, yena tathāgato atīte buddhe "
"parinibbute chinnapapañce chinnavaṭume pariyādinnavaṭṭe sabbadukkhavītivatte "
"jātitopi anussarati, nāmatopi anussarati, gottatopi anussarati, "
"āyuppamāṇatopi anussarati, sāvakayugatopi anussarati, sāvakasannipātatopi "
"anussarati ‘evaṃjaccā te bhagavanto ahesuṃ’ itipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.33.4"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃnāmā evaṅgottā evaṃsīlā evaṃdhammā evaṃpaññā evaṃvihārī evaṃvimuttā te "
"bhagavanto ahesuṃ’ itipī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc185"></a>
msgctxt "dn14:3.33.5"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn14:3.33.6"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn14:3.33.7"
msgid "Mahāpadānasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
